&gt;，但仍然很危险。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;大风可能会限制消防员从地面和空中扑灭 Palisades 和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=454f1cca7f984c3ca84992873011aa79&amp;amp;_e=wEHfPNo8VPWYrAyGSwEfetHGFnkqPZAihCetAzXMOETTSg7eU1oJ0bNR9TR3ARc0gMYgMyj5D8_nZBe97Xxg7d-hvXUhpeqE8uK6_QO-CFxb_QLzbaGvPgDUeYx41PzKLgr7FGmFSG7Bw2p0hxxkOPAEdBD6VE_1r2N7oZkVzmZanWskwYZ6RDmvBLWldd3fBcjpwyYiZA9E-Ian5_7EV6qhWiyeHPRZndNt7RIHoaAKdtQfH0-WJZyPV_te-vNOg82OG4m4X7Co1XY3CK69-5AdR-UrREAq18UGvUx2fsw9cQRBLtFcE1RnNDRwWGpbTwrXysMAXosYywVOdZazog%3D%3D" target="_blank" title="加州消防局网站"&gt;Eaton 火灾&lt;/a&gt;的机会。大火烧毁了近 40,000 英亩土地，从海岸上的太平洋帕利塞德到圣盖博山脚下的阿尔塔迪纳，整个社区都被夷为平地。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;预计 2,772 平方英里（7,179 平方公里）的范围内将出现极端火灾，阵风将火焰搅动，其风速与上周引发火灾的风速相似。未来几天，该地区将有超过 800 万人面临严重的火灾天气。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;请在 Bloomberg.com 上阅读&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=454f1cca7f984c3ca84992873011aa79&amp;amp;_e=wEHfPNo8VPWYrAyGSwEfeoEXgUO7jCxlt0a0560sx91H6W-oUHbpkDucHM5bptbQvNtltXt9k_HR-ZGY7AkPmE76GE5lX4p7eIfwimSWoL_9bCSnm6DWLZqDoYPc61foGTM1kIXnc7qqxhBzlC8b_iJfE4HJnIeB1XeZd4zZYudGPMYF-Mk0tDauFxdxsZIEzOd5Jl_v8KVRAHOjiDuq3iEDbstV2ml39ZM3GiNpjqJFQb1RUsdgJZbm0Dwvpl3xSdX3Ek8pYjEpDkY5TjBb3IqpZ5DqbWhU0qyr7DE4xL1AXZWUOUf-N9yc_jRXRgB8YOG8Zi4MuIB-J1P2NNWXsg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;全文&lt;/a&gt;。如需直接发送到您收件箱的天气见解， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=454f1cca7f984c3ca84992873011aa79&amp;amp;_e=wEHfPNo8VPWYrAyGSwEfeiE6pEBv3HoD9k6uZisABwviC0WQByrzEPcUST7hngpY1c7akxN08TNKlSePMns81lFdHfmydyUrTagylz5B24Xv7aGuFE8emDUgOsn3rQGW6OReoHL_SITL-1kAh7MrXkc-34HEGPnDXr4KzNSKI1DPT410QBmm1a1RW8WQXy9faXqTzzcngAHABFMSLIpZRHx7j3ArAZe2_ed5Zw5IwPN-CyUu_AflaWgHUa_HPP336SUKrp5uAUzVf84a2jpqopU9K_K1l_fILz2tnxzadx0qakzbnSq6Q2jzMpkDlO